This is how to choose_num of x and y:
   When x is more than y, then:
      The answer is diff of 0 and 1
   End when
   Remember that n is y
   When remainder of y and 2 is 1, then:
      Remember that n is diff of y and 1
   End when
   When n is less than x, then:
      The answer is diff of 0 and 1
   End when
   The answer is n
